{
  "texts": [
    "They use the feature mean of the pre-trained Perceiver Resampler as the image representation and the EOS token of the pre-trained BioGPT as the text representation.",
    "A contrastive loss then aligns both feature vectors in the common embedding space.",
    "For HistoCLIP we used the same loss as for CLIP 56.",
    "For HistoSigLIP we used the loss proposed in SigLIP 57.",
    "To improve performance and avoid training instabilities, we froze the vision encoder during training."
  ]
}